---
import "./CardImplement.css";
---

<article class="round no-elevate p-0 wave">
  <div class="gfx gfx-implement" role="img" aria-label="Three blocks rising and settling into a stack, suggesting construction">
    <span class="block b1"></span>
    <span class="block b2"></span>
    <span class="block b3"></span>
  </div>
  <div class="p-5">
    <h3 class="text-3 lh-2 fw-6">Implement</h3>
    <p class=" mt-2 text-1 italic">For startups and growing teams.</p>
    <p class="text-0 mt-2">You have a problem AI could solve. We work alongside your team to design, build, and ship it. Not a demo. Not a prototype destined for a shelf. A working system your people actually use.</p>
  </div>
</article>
